summary: A collection of unit tests that verify the functionality of graph data structures and operations, including creation from various input formats (edge list, CSR, COO, NetworkX, SciPy), edge queries, format conversions, mutation handling, and properties such as multigraph support and sorting.
business_intent: To ensure reliable and correct handling of graph representations and operations within the compute module, guaranteeing compatibility with multiple data formats and robust graph manipulation capabilities.
